Upgrading lightbox:
-------------------

Upgrading the lightbox code is pretty simple:

- Download lightbox from http://www.huddletogether.com/projects/lightbox2/
- Unpack the downloaded zip file.
- Move the unpacked files to the code subdirectory.

The resulting code subdirectory should now look like:

code/
    css/
        lightbox.css
    images/
        blank.gif
        closelabel.gif
        close.gif
        image-1.jpg
        loading.gif
        nextlabel.gif
        next.gif
        prevlabel.gif
        prev.gif
        thumb-1.jpg
    index.html
    js/
        effects.js
        lightbox.js
        prototype.js
        scriptaculous.js

